*assp-1.2.6-r3 (03 Feb 2007)

  03 Feb 2007; William L. Thomson Jr. <wltjr@gentoo.org>
  -assp-1.2.6-r2.ebuild, +assp-1.2.6-r3.ebuild:
  Added some sed to fix upstream bug, PopB4SMTPMerak -> $PopB4SMTPMerak in an
  if statement, booo

